pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-20%2021%3A34%3A12%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2031572053&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=g3uGB96MX3qdbcaGt74FHVOZFXQ%3D" alt="" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">今年，122名考上研究生的录取院校包括西南大学、安徽大学、暨南大学、福州大学、西南财经大学、南昌大学、江西师范大学、江西财经大学等65所国内高校以及昆士兰大学、悉尼大学、利物浦大学、泰莱大学等多所国外高校。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-21%2009%3A10%3A07356.jpg?Expires=2031613808&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=fX0%2B9tEvwttzKpYmVdFhKPcFz%2FQ%3D" alt="" width="650" height="336" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">范红铭代表学校向考取研究生的同学表示热烈的祝贺！向精心施教、助力学生成功的老师表示诚挚的谢意！他指出，考研，作为高等教育的重要一环，对于个人和社会的发展都具有不可忽视的重要性。学校高度重视考研工作，将其视为提高人才培养质量、推动学校内涵式发展的重要抓手，不断优化考研服务体系，加强考研指导，集中教学资源和有关力量创造良好的考研学习和生活条件。他向正在准备考研的同学提出了建议和希望：一是明确目标，早做准备；二是制定计划，科学备考；三是树立自信、贵在坚持；四是形成良好的学习氛围。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: a