ding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-05-20%2021%3A50%3A54%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2031573055&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=lJqeMrsaAaBshWzfAp0qBvuX5Co%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 28pt; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: base